<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>01</p>
<p><strong>若要做一个宵夜美食打榜</strong></p>
<p><strong>作为流量爱豆的它</strong></p>
<p><strong>肯定是妥妥的C位出道</strong></p>
<p><strong>低调朴实，只在暗夜窜动的它</strong></p>
<p><strong>虽不屑市俗的名利纷争</strong></p>
<p><strong>但江湖一直流传着，有关它的传说</strong></p>
<p><strong>烧烤一出，谁与针锋？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>烧 /烤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">磨西烧烤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远近闻名</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">暗红的炭火烧得很旺</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上到牛羊肉、下到蔬菜杂碎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在炭火的高温滋养下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">溢出的黄油，滋滋作响</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">掺夹着辣椒、花椒、孜然的香味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漂浮在磨西古镇的上方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200804/968ed907f1a6419ea52cf7d9a7f7cf00.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每条马路、每片街区、每栋老楼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大排档小餐馆店铺上空</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都飘浮着着各种诱人的香气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不同于白天的清幽安静</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夜晚的磨西镇完全是另外一副模样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">激情野莽，充满人间烟火气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200804/9267693616f94b4ead4baaad067383fb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>在万物皆可烤的时代，小编今天就给大家扒扒海螺沟的深夜美食</strong></p>
<p>1</p>
<p>木屋烤鸡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">选用海螺沟土生土养的鸡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 用当地特有的树木柴烧制</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烧烤师傅的功底在于对火候的拿捏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就需要有人在火堆旁，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不停的来回翻转烤鸡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烤出的肉食外酥里嫩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200804/9d05a33ee2a7415ca7b715355a547369.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“吭哧吭哧”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嘬取油辣的鸡肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再舔几下手指头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就连骨头缝儿里的肉丝也不放过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200804/8e49defa15124c38893237a8930a08ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡皮是精华所在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">富含胶原蛋白的皮下组织</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在炭火的滋烤下，色泽金黄酥脆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200804/22826ae8fb5343ca957ca4abca0f2c63.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“叮咚”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是啤酒杯在烧烤摊前，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发出碰撞的声响</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一如食客们现在的心情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">酣畅淋漓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200804/acaead4bd5cf4c4fbb81757146c3f960.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">啤酒清冽甘甜的酒味滑入食道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一呼吸，连空气都是透心凉的爽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烤鸡配啤酒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是什么神仙日子？</p>
<p>2</p>
<p>烤肉串</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>小香猪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最为海螺沟美食链顶端</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃最丰腴的草</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喝富含多种矿物质的冰川水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长最健康的肉，才能成为签上肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200804/ff6690de33b740f597c1e3a867b20bb0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一大把竹签大肉串整齐排列在铁架上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">调料和油在木刷的摆动下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">充分融入鲜嫩的肉质里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">受热混合后滴入木炭中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一滴两滴，滋滋作响</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200804/fa760dbe46eb42c9956b6d53e3f06888.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等到六七成熟后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再撒上海螺沟人最爱的<strong>辣椒粉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是有外地朋友</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你得提前说加一把<strong>孜然</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">店家就会按你的喜好烤制</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200804/a47b345fc83a402094c1bdacf116901d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等烤好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">端盘上菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“哎哟诶”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那香气简直一绝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闻着，哈达子就已经流出来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200804/c52549af2f9f4a77ba21921d8567bd10.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>3</p>
<p>烤乳猪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">提到小香猪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就不能不说烤乳猪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">反复用干草将猪毛烧尽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">涂上秘制的香料进行腌制</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200804/0dc645411cb345d6bdc32cf0d962312a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">支上铁架</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用苹果木、桃木、香杉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">先勐火去水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再用木炭火慢慢烤制</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鲜嫩肥美的香味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肉质Q弹，嚼劲十足的猪蹄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在高温下一点点渗出金黄的油汁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200804/3df32037db6d40c8ae2c1fb6d143e224.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">害怕变老？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不存在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>来海螺沟啃香猪腿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>补充胶原蛋白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200804/3f83bde1115c4ca792cc0c9a88dbfa71.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>4</p>
<p>蒜蓉茄子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蒜蓉、麻辣、十三香</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">外加小葱、香菜，和折耳根</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">硕大浑圆的茄子，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">展开自己的肚皮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接纳酸甜麻辣的各种配料</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200804/e780ebea252b44cd81392e60272d1d79.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在锡纸铁盘里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伴随跳动的火焰，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">穿越时间的发酵周期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与各路水火不容的食材</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相濡以沫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“撕拉”</strong>一声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竹筷在茄子身上轻轻撕开一道口子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">早已吸饱了油脂的茄子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">溢出一道香辣鲜红的油脂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200804/4e1b2405ef9d4e1685836034059e5515.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>5</p>
<p>烤土豆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烤土豆是海螺沟最朴素的食物</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但你可别小看它</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">麻雀虽小，五脏俱全</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小小的土豆里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蕴含着大大的人生哲理</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它是老一代人的时代烙印</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是新一代人潮流吃法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200804/c310acdaf1074aa394b85a5c6bafd5b8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从泥土里挖新鲜的土豆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">搓去泥土</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接放入火堆里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烤上8-9分钟后即可剥皮而食</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200804/ac97060106e244e8a68b3e5612352d5c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拌上当地特有的<strong>胡椒面、干海椒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那味道简直不摆了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200804/57849eab1bb447f2a4af16ba46d61064.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>6</p>
<p>解暑神器——冰粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在川人心里，深藏着一个观念</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“无冰粉，不夏天”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冰滑透明似镜像的冰粉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">倒上熬制粘稠的红糖水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">葡萄干、醪糟汤圆、银耳......</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全部一股脑儿掺杂在冰粉里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200804/26c42a5860b84c3fae1bc1d799e2694b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>吸熘吸熘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仰头举着冰粉碗一饮而尽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爽滑清凉的冰粉儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自舌尖处，滑向食道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">精妙绝美的口感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一不小心很容易咬到舌头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200804/b32fa1725e5c4302867f578dad8de5db.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老板来2碗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老板还是先来5碗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老板再来7碗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">.......</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们的深夜食堂 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中国人的深夜食堂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是在精致的居酒屋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是在街角巷尾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小餐馆、大排档、烧烤摊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200804/49e3481f42704164990ce1727994cb58.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">穿裤衩，拖鞋的大叔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喷着阿玛尼香水的时尚先生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瞪着高跟鞋的红唇美女</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刚加班回家的实习生</p>
